28
00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:32.800
Justice, O royal duke!

29
00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:33.730
Vail your regard

30
00:01:33.730 --> 00:01:35.600
Upon a wrong'd,

31
00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:38.670
I would fain have said, amaid!

32
00:01:38.670 --> 00:01:40.800
O worthy prince, dishonournot your eye

33
00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:42.630
