36
00:01:51.330 --> 00:01:55.000
Relate your wrongs; inwhat? by whom? be brief.

37
00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:56.470
Here is Lord Angelo shallgive you justice:

38
00:01:56.470 --> 00:01:57.570
Reveal yourself to him.

39
00:01:57.570 --> 00:01:58.500
O worthy prince,

40
00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:01.270
You bid me seek redemptionof the devil:

41
00:02:01.270 --> 00:02:03.400
Hear me yourself; for thatwhich I must speak

42
00:02:03.400 --> 00:02:05.030
