43
00:02:05.030 --> 00:02:06.870
Or wring redress from you.

44
00:02:06.870 --> 00:02:09.600
Hear me, O hear me, here!

45
00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:12.370
My lord, her wits, I fearme, are not firm:

46
00:02:12.370 --> 00:02:14.330
