61
00:02:49.370 --> 00:02:50.500
Away with her!

62
00:02:50.500 --> 00:02:52.800
Poor soul, She speaks thisin the infirmity of sense.

63
00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:55.130
O prince, I conjure thee,

64
00:02:55.130 --> 00:02:56.000
as thou believest

65
00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.070
There is another comfortthan this world,

66
00:02:58.070 --> 00:02:59.400
